    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>今天炸了，没多少分，悲催……</p><h1 id="模拟赛"><a href="#模拟赛" class="headerlink" title="模拟赛"></a>模拟赛</h1><h2 id="失误"><a href="#失误" class="headerlink" title="失误"></a>失误</h2><ul><li><p>T1思考时间过久导致后三题暴力时间紧张</p></li><li><p>T1深搜RE，枚举量太大理所当然</p></li><li><p>T2 MLE，<strong>二维数组至多开 $10^4$ ！！</strong></p></li></ul><h2 id="T1-区间"><a href="#T1-区间" class="headerlink" title="T1 区间"></a>T1 区间</h2><h3 id="题意理解"><a href="#题意理解" class="headerlink" title="题意理解"></a>题意理解</h3><p>有 $n$ 个区间，端点为 $[l_i,r_i]$ 。需要删除一些区间使得：</p><ul><li><p>所有区间的数值被划分成<strong>恰好两个不重叠的部分</strong>。</p></li><li><p>对于两个有公共数值的区间，它们在同一个部分中。</p></li></ul><p>求满足条件的最小删除数量。</p><h3 id="朴素算法-45pts"><a href="#朴素算法-45pts" class="headerlink" title="朴素算法 - 45pts"></a>朴素算法 - 45pts</h3><p>枚举一个数 $x$ ，将所有包含 $x$ 的区间（即 $l_i \le x &lt; r_i$ ）去除即可满足条件。使用差分统计这样的区间数即可。</p><h3 id="正解"><a href="#正解" class="headerlink" title="正解"></a>正解</h3><p>基于 <code>算法1</code> ，发现可以成为 $x$ 的节点一定是一个区间的端点。所以将所有点离散化后枚举，时间复杂度 $O(n \log n)$</p><h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> N=<span class="hljs-number">2e5</span>,INF=<span class="hljs-number">0x3f3f3f3f</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> l[N<span class="hljs-number">+5</span>],r[N<span class="hljs-number">+5</span>],b[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*N<span class="hljs-number">+5</span>];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> t;<br>cin&gt;&gt;t;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(t--)&#123;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">memset</span>(b,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">sizeof</span>(b));<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>cin&gt;&gt;n;<br>vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; tmp;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxl=-INF,minr=INF;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;<br>cin&gt;&gt;l[i]&gt;&gt;r[i];<br>tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(l[i]);<br>tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(r[i]);<br>maxl=<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(maxl,l[i]),minr=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(minr,r[i]);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">sort</span>(tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>());<br>tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">resize</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">unique</span>(tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>())-tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>());<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;<br>l[i]=<span class="hljs-built_in">lower_bound</span>(tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>(),l[i])-tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>()<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>;<br>r[i]=<span class="hljs-built_in">lower_bound</span>(tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>(),tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">end</span>(),r[i])-tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>()<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>;<br>b[l[i]]++,b[r[i]]--;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> ans=INF;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,s=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();i++)&#123;<br>s+=b[i];<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(minr&lt;=tmp[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]&amp;&amp;tmp[i]&lt;=maxl)<br>ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(ans,s);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(ans==INF)<br>cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-1&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;endl;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>cout&lt;&lt;ans&lt;&lt;endl;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="T2-染色"><a href="#T2-染色" class="headerlink" title="T2 染色"></a>T2 染色</h3><h3 id="题意理解-1"><a href="#题意理解-1" class="headerlink" title="题意理解"></a>题意理解</h3><h3 id="朴素算法-75pts"><a href="#朴素算法-75pts" class="headerlink" title="朴素算法 - 75pts"></a>朴素算法 - 75pts</h3><p>设 $g_{i,j}$ 为第 $i$ 行的第 $j$ 列的颜色。根据题意，有 $g_{i,j} &#x3D; g_{i-1,j} \oplus g_{i,j-1} \oplus g_{i-1,j-1}$ 。所以，确定第一行与第一列时整个矩阵都可以被确定，直接输出 $2^{n+m-1}$ 即可。能处理无询问的情况，结合爆搜处理询问可得 $75 \text {pts}$ 。</p><h3 id="正解-1"><a href="#正解-1" class="headerlink" title="正解"></a>正解</h3><p>可以发现在朴素算法过程中，每次询问即加入一个判断条件：“如果 $x$ 行 $1$ 列为 $a$ ，$1$ 行 $y$ 列为 $b$ ，则 &lt;*进行计算*&gt;”</p><p>设每行每列有两个点 $u_0, u_1$ ，表示取值为 $0&#x2F;1$ ，把上文限制看作加入边，维护连通块的数量，每个连通块中的点必须同时计算。</p><p>具体来说，设两个点 $u,v$ ，连上 $u_0 \to v_c, u_1 \to v_{1-c}$ ，若此时存在一个点使 $u_0, u_1$ 在同一连通块中，则答案为 $0$ 。可以使用<em>并查集</em>维护，并特判 $x&#x3D;1$ 或 $y&#x3D;1$ 时的情况，时间复杂度 $O(n \alpha(n))$ 。</p><h3 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><p>可恶的卡常题！！！</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;cstdio&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;cstring&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;numeric&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;string&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> ll;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> N=<span class="hljs-number">2e6</span><span class="hljs-number">+5</span>,Mod=<span class="hljs-number">1e9</span><span class="hljs-number">+7</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> f[N],cnt;<br>ll p[N];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">find</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> f[x]==x?x:f[x]=<span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>(f[x]);&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">merge</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> x,<span class="hljs-type">int</span> y)</span></span>&#123;<br>x=<span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>(x),y=<span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>(y);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(x==y) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>f[x]=y,cnt--;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br>ios::<span class="hljs-built_in">sync_with_stdio</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>cin.<span class="hljs-built_in">tie</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>),cout.<span class="hljs-built_in">tie</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n,m,q;<br>cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;m&gt;&gt;q;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">iota</span>(f<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>,f<span class="hljs-number">+2</span>*(n+m)<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>p[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,cnt=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*(n+m);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n+m;i++)<br>p[i]=p[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]*<span class="hljs-number">2</span>%Mod;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> flag=<span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>cout&lt;&lt;p[cnt/<span class="hljs-number">2</span><span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(q--)&#123;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x,y,c;<br>cin&gt;&gt;x&gt;&gt;y&gt;&gt;c;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(flag)&#123;<br>cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">merge</span>(x,y+n+c*(n+m));<br><span class="hljs-built_in">merge</span>(x+n+m,y+n+(c^<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)*(n+m));<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>(x)==<span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>(x+n+m))&#123;<br>cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>flag=<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>&#125;<br>cout&lt;&lt;p[cnt/<span class="hljs-number">2</span><span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
